Top Stories (January 22)

CALPX ANNOUNCES IT WILL PERMANENTLY CLOSE DOWN BY APRIL
California's five-year-old experiment with electricity deregulation saw its 
first casualty Friday with an announcement by the state's Power Exchange that 
it would permanently shut down its trading operation by April.
http://199.97.97.79/IMDS%PMADJN0%read%/home/content/users/imds/feeds/djn/2001/
01/22/eng-djn/eng-djn_112027_16_4014022634365

CALIFORNIA WEARILY FACES ANOTHER WEEK OF POWER SHORTAGES
California wearily faces another week of power problems after a weekend that 
was supposed to provide relief resulted only in alerts of impending shortages.
http://199.97.97.79/IMDS%PMADJN0%read%/home/content/users/imds/feeds/djn/2001/
01/22/eng-djn/eng-djn_092033_211_907312117983

BUSH NOMINATES HEBERT FOR ENERGY
President Bush named Curt Hebert, who has argued against federal involvement 
in the California electricity crisis, as chairman of the agency that 
regulates wholesale power markets.
http://199.97.97.163/IMDS%PMANAT0%read%/home/content/users/imds/feeds/comtex/2
001/01/22/ao/0000-1961-bush-electricity

DOW CHEMICAL, AMERICAN ELECTRIC POWER PLAN $325M LOUISIANA PLANT
American Electric Power Co. and Dow Chemical Co. signed definitive agreements 
that will lead to the construction of a $325 million cogeneration plant at 
Dow Chemical's Plaquemine, La., chemical complex.
http://199.97.97.79/IMDS%PMADJN0%read%/home/content/users/imds/feeds/djn/2001/
01/22/eng-djn/eng-djn_120036_42_4477495579049

CONSTRUCTION UNDERWAY ON 25.5-MW WISCONSIN WIND FARM
FPL Energy LLC has started work on a 25.5 megawatt wind farm in Iowa County, 
Wisconsin, the company said Monday.
http://199.97.97.79/IMDS%PMADJN0%read%/home/content/users/imds/feeds/djn/2001/
01/22/eng-djn/eng-djn_162027_123_977932417765

ENERGY MERGER DANCE GATHERS MOMENTUM
The great merger dance in Western Canada's energy patch is gathering 
momentum. The past few weeks have seen the announcement of several takeover 
bids, both friendly and otherwise.
http://199.97.97.163/IMDS%PMANAT0%read%/home/content/users/imds/feeds/smallcap
center/2001/01/22/eng-smallcapcenter/eng-smallcapcenter_162234_110_47611941350
